{
  "stem": "6878.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a football space.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody come out from there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that, that day, we lost about 10,000 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were standing four in a queue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] you know, division.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the people from left, the Lithuanian army used to straightaway take them away and pack them into trucks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the next morning they were shot on the-- we lost 10,000, more than 10,000 people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We lost on the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were shot to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the fact I know is that one was not shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He fell amongst the, the dead, but he wasn't shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I met him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He came back to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I met him after, and he told me that story, that the Russian prisoners of war used to dig trenches, long, long trenches.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the Jews were driven past their machine guns, and they were thrown into the-- and they were then with, with, with, with machines, trucks, covered with soil and finished.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was amongst the one who he wasn't shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He just fell into it with the-- he came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we know that they're dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Was after announced that more than-- we lost more than 10,000 people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it is also in that newspaper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He, he then shouted out-- what I want to say is, [SPEAKING GERMAN]-- the German shouted out [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It means me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had many occasions like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them, in the summertime, they used to allow us to, to go and have a swim in the river.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the hot day, sometimes they used to let us go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] beside the ghetto, if we come to the airport, I didn't say that I was sent once from the barracks.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
